messages.message: Hi :wave: we’ve gotten feedback that field suggestions could be improved. If you have any example docs where the suggestions are not good, can you share them here?
cc @Matt Weaver @Lee you mentioned you saw many docs were the suggestions weren’t great

@lydia On this document, which I picked because the person’s name is large, there’s an angled set of text and a straightforward table. The text at the top is skewed to an angle. Therefore the initial fields and the initial extractions are off.
